5
00:00:51,759 --> 00:00:54,159
You want me to fall out with those factory owners in the north of the city,

6
00:00:55,240 --> 00:00:56,600
completely burn all bridges with them?

7
00:00:57,159 --> 00:00:57,719
Boss Huo,

8
